snippet.title: Chuck E Cheese Family Fun Indoor Play Area and Activities for Children Kids Video
snippet.description:
Family Fun at Chuck E. Cheese, kids first time at Chuck E Cheeses! Toddlers playing arcade games and indoor playground!

Riding on train rides and race cars with Chucky in the passenger seat, it was an exciting day for these kids on their first time ever to a place like Chucky Cheese.  There was an indoor playground with a crawl tube and some slides, lots of fun arcade games to play and cool rides for the kids. 

Most people have taken their kids to Chuckee Cheese before and know how much fun it is for kids.  There is so much noise and fun games going on with the puppets and crazy animatronic characters, my favorite was the rock band that came out and started playing music.  

Gathering tickets was a new experience for the kids, as they learned how to earn them from winning games and arcade games, while being able to pick out colorful gifts and surprises at the end of their trip to Chuckee CHeeses.  Lots of opportunity for family fun in the indoor play area and arcade!

snippet.description:
This is the indoor playground Lek & Luft in Kristinehamn, Sweden. The indoor play area features lots of inflatable attractions, like bouncy castles, slides, and several obstacle courses. You can also dress up in sumo suits and have a wrestling match.

This was so much fun!

Indoor playground fun for family and kids.
